local Tool = script.Parent
local Plr = game:GetService("Players").LocalPlayer local Mouse = Plr:GetMouse() local Char = Plr.Character local Hum = Char:WaitForChild("Humanoid")
local GunUI = Tool:WaitForChild("GunUI") GunUI.ReloadBtn.Visible = game:GetService("UserInputService").TouchEnabled
local Crosshair = script:WaitForChild("Crosshair")
local Fire = Tool:WaitForChild("Fire")
local Settings = Tool:WaitForChild("Settings") local Ammo = Settings.Ammo local MaxAmmo = Ammo.Value local AmmoReserve = Settings.ReserveAmmo local ReloadTime = Settings.ReloadTime
GunUI.TextLabel.Text = AmmoReserve.Value.."/"..Ammo.Value
local WaitTime = Settings.WaitTime local Debounce = false
local Equipped = false
local function Reload() if Equipped == true then if AmmoReserve.Value > 0 then if not Debounce then Debounce = true
Tool.Handle.Reload:Play() GunUI.TextLabel.Text = "Reloading..."
wait(ReloadTime.Value)
Ammo.Value = MaxAmmo AmmoReserve.Value -= 1 GunUI.TextLabel.Text = AmmoReserve.Value.."/"..Ammo.Value
Debounce = false end end end end
local function FireRemote() Tool.Handle.Click:Play() if Ammo.Value > 0 then if not Debounce then Debounce = true
Ammo.Value -= 1 GunUI.TextLabel.Text = AmmoReserve.Value.."/"..Ammo.Value
local MHit = Plr:GetMouse().Hit Fire:FireServer(MHit)
wait(WaitTime.Value) Debounce = false end else Reload() end end
local function EquipToggle() if not Equipped then Equipped = true GunUI.Parent = Plr.PlayerGui GunUI = Plr.PlayerGui:FindFirstChild("GunUI") Mouse.Icon = Crosshair.Texture else Equipped = false GunUI.Parent = Tool Mouse.Icon = " " end end
Tool.Activated:Connect(FireRemote)
Tool.Equipped:Connect(EquipToggle) Tool.Unequipped:Connect(EquipToggle)
game:GetService("UserInputService").InputBegan:Connect(function(key) if key.KeyCode == Enum.KeyCode.R then Reload() end end)
GunUI.ReloadBtn.Activated:Connect(Reload)

local Tool = script.Parent
local Fire = Tool.Fire local Settings = Tool.Settings
local Damage = Settings.Damage local Range = Settings.Range
local Handle = Tool.Handle
local Raycastparams = RaycastParams.new() Raycastparams.RespectCanCollide = false
local function Shoot(plr,MHit) Handle.FireSound:Play() Raycastparams.FilterDescendantsInstances = {Tool.Parent,Tool} Raycastparams.FilterType = Enum.RaycastFilterType.Exclude
local OriginPoint = Handle.Position local Direction = (MHit.Position - OriginPoint).Unit
local BulletHit = workspace:Raycast(OriginPoint,Direction * 1000,Raycastparams)
local Distance = (MHit.Position- OriginPoint).Magnitude
wait(Distance*0.0025) if BulletHit ~= nil then local Hit = BulletHit.Instance
if Distance < Range.Value then --print(Hit) if Hit.Parent:FindFirstChild("Humanoid") then local TargetHumanoid = Hit.Parent.Humanoid TargetHumanoid:TakeDamage(Damage.Value) end end end end
Fire.OnServerEvent:Connect(Shoot)
